cdata.name: USDC
cdata.desc:
USDC is a cryptocurrency payment platform. It allows users to perform transactions using the blockchain technology on a global scale with the platform native token, the USDC. in addition, a digital wallet is available on USDC for the users to store and manage their digital assets.

The USDC token is an Ethereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is a stable coin that will serve the users as a medium to exchange value on the platform. According to USDC Price Guarantee Plan, it uses the company as a guarantee, each USDC reserve on the platform will equal 1 USD of ETH or BTC forever.
